  "title": "Two multicolor bright lights were seen hovering over Brasília [2001]**",
  "URL": "http://brazilianufoarchives.com/2020/06/12/two-multicolor-bright-lights-were-seen-hovering-over-brasilia-2001/",
  "short_URL": "https://wp.me/pc3ctW-mz",
  "content": "<p style=\"text-align:justify;\"><strong>MARCH 25th, 2001</strong>. Time: 04h09pm. Duration: 35 seconds. In Brasília, Distrito Federal, four (4) witnesses spotted two (2) unidentified flying objects looking like multicolor lights. The UFOs hovered above the southeastern sector of Brasília and about 2 km apart from each other. The bright objects were observed under good visibility conditions and no photos or videos were made. There were no reports of trails or condensation marks left by the UFOs in their trajectory either.</p>\n<p style=\"text-align:justify;\"><span style=\"font-family:Verdana;font-size:small;color:#808000;\"><em>Cf.</em> ARQUIVO NACIONAL (Brasil). Sistema de Informações do Arquivo Nacional (SIAN). Fundo &#8216;Objeto Voador Não Identificado (OVNI)&#8217;. Código de Referência BR DFANBSB ARX.0.0.604. &#8220;</span><span style=\"font-family:Verdana;font-size:small;color:#808000;\">Questionário sobre avistamento de ovni em Brasília, Distrito Federal&#8221;. Brasília, DF. 1952 a 2015. Último acesso realizado em 27/05/2020.</span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align:justify;\"><em><span style=\"font-family:Verdana;font-size:small;color:#808000;\">The BRAZILIAN UFO ARCHIVES website is a private initiative and IS NOT endorsed or sponsored by the Arquivo Nacional do Brasil [see our &#8216;Info&#8217; page]. </span></em><span style=\"font-family:Verdana;font-size:small;color:#808000;\"><em>*THE ORIGINAL FILE WITH THE CASE REFERRED TO IN THIS TEXT CAN BE FOUND IN THE DOCUMENTAL COLLECTION OF “ARQUIVO NACIONAL DO BRASIL, LOCATED IN THE “OBJETO VOADOR NÃO IDENTIFICADO (OVNI)” FUND, UNDER THE REFERENCE CODE [&#8220;Código de Referência&#8221;] MENTIONED ABOVE.</em> <strong><a style=\"color:#808000;\" href=\"http://sian.an.gov.br/sianex/consulta/login.asp\">HERE IS THE LINK TO SEARCH THEIR WEBSITE</a></strong></span><span style=\"font-family:Verdana;font-size:small;color:#808000;\"> </span></p>\n",
